{"word":"G102 - ἀδύνατος - adýnatos - ad-oo'-nat-os - Could not do","slug":"G102","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀδύνατος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>adýnatos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ad-oo'-nat-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Could not do"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03B4;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - adunatos</b> - <i>ad-oo'-nat-os</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G1415\">G1415</a>; <i>unable</i>, that is, <i>weak</i> (literally or figuratively); passively <i>impossible:</i> - could not do, impossible, impotent, not possible, weak."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G101\">G101</a>, <a href=\"#/G1410\">G1410</a>, <a href=\"#/G1411\">G1411</a>, <a href=\"#/G1412\">G1412</a>, <a href=\"#/G1413\">G1413</a>, <a href=\"#/G1414\">G1414</a>, <a href=\"#/G1415\">G1415</a>, <a href=\"#/G1743\">G1743</a>"}]}